// AddTodoDialog
// Modal dialog for adding a new project todo item. Collects a title and
// optional description. Confirms on Cmd/Ctrl+Enter or the OK button.

FUNCTION AddTodoDialog(onClose, onConfirm) -> JSX                      EXPORT
  Manages title and description state.
  Keyboard: Escape closes; Cmd/Ctrl+Enter calls handleConfirm.

---

FUNCTION handleConfirm() -> void
  Calls onConfirm(title, description) only if title is non-empty. Closes.

---

FUNCTION handleKeyDown(e) -> void
  Escape -> closes. Cmd/Ctrl+Enter -> handleConfirm.
